    {
      "number": 5,
      "id": "I_kwDOHulKFM5R1vvI",
      "title": "define configuration attributes for STAR and non-STAR flows",
      "url": "https://github.com/FredericFi/cdni-wg/issues/5",
      "state": "CLOSED",
      "author": "thomas-fossati",
      "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
      "assignees": [
        "thomas-fossati"
      ],
      "labels": [],
      "body": "The idea is to have the uCDN providing hints for the dCDN order request.\r\n\r\n* For STAR orders, the [`auto-renewal`](https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc8739.html#section-5.4) properties:\r\n\r\n```json\r\n\"acme-star-hints\" : {\r\n  \"start-date\": \"\",\r\n  \"end-date\": \"\",\r\n  \"lifetime\": \"\",\r\n  \"lifetime-adjust\": \"\",\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n* For non-STAR orders, there doesn't seem to be anything specific for the time being.",
      "createdAt": "2022-09-14T14:02:50Z",
      "updatedAt": "2022-10-12T14:18:16Z",
      "closedAt": "2022-10-12T14:18:16Z",
      "comments": [
        {
          "author": "thomas-fossati",
          "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
          "body": "We need to decide whether these hints should be part of the ACME delegation object (alongside the CSR template and optional CNAME mappings), or of the CDNI interface.\r\n\r\nWe should involve @yaronf.",
          "createdAt": "2022-09-27T12:42:35Z",
          "updatedAt": "2022-09-27T12:42:35Z"
        },
        {
          "author": "smishra1200",
          "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
          "body": "Hi Thomas - Thanks for the updates. Sure, do you want to add Yaron in\nGithub or Fred will need to him?\n\nThanks\nSanjay\n\nOn Tue, Sep 27, 2022 at 8:42 AM Thomas Fossati ***@***.***>\nwrote:\n\n> We need to decide whether these hints should be part of the ACME\n> delegation object (alongside the CSR template and optional CNAME mappings),\n> or of the CDNI interface.\n>\n> We should involve @yaronf\n> <https://urldefense.proofpoint.com/v2/url?u=https-3A__github.com_yaronf&d=DwMCaQ&c=udBTRvFvXC5Dhqg7UHpJlPps3mZ3LRxpb6__0PomBTQ&r=XniVbishGiO2Ao9hKqSc-hTVIWCi3T-x6GdHR4ZTgoM&m=khMltZMp26qyr3o_tjRmLcqmFd_VOy9GzX4ua4-tjMjAGosxh3I1ulaZXpxet9Zg&s=esXEfECx-Dax6ndFYwrr-IY0-M1R9pKzZspXjD9SPSM&e=>\n> .\n>\n> \u2014\n> Reply to this email directly, view it on GitHub\n> <https://urldefense.proofpoint.com/v2/url?u=https-3A__github.com_FredericFi_cdni-2Dwg_issues_5-23issuecomment-2D1259451418&d=DwMCaQ&c=udBTRvFvXC5Dhqg7UHpJlPps3mZ3LRxpb6__0PomBTQ&r=XniVbishGiO2Ao9hKqSc-hTVIWCi3T-x6GdHR4ZTgoM&m=khMltZMp26qyr3o_tjRmLcqmFd_VOy9GzX4ua4-tjMjAGosxh3I1ulaZXpxet9Zg&s=pBxk6anSiydJ5ZeSX_Uk8_gtMch6YteJjxE-X-U3jtc&e=>,\n> or unsubscribe\n> <https://urldefense.proofpoint.com/v2/url?u=https-3A__github.com_notifications_unsubscribe-2Dauth_ABGNJTANEK5X3JVA5WPIBRDWALTUNANCNFSM6AAAAAAQMONMLY&d=DwMCaQ&c=udBTRvFvXC5Dhqg7UHpJlPps3mZ3LRxpb6__0PomBTQ&r=XniVbishGiO2Ao9hKqSc-hTVIWCi3T-x6GdHR4ZTgoM&m=khMltZMp26qyr3o_tjRmLcqmFd_VOy9GzX4ua4-tjMjAGosxh3I1ulaZXpxet9Zg&s=WNFA9ORx8nXsifm4Sg0u3QRKqnvMyRrx4E13u6i4VZI&e=>\n> .\n> You are receiving this because you are subscribed to this thread.Message\n> ID: ***@***.***>\n>\n",
