      "body": "Note: inserting C-style comments in the JSON examples will fail validation.\r\nIf we need to add contextual explanations about an example, that should be done in the surrounding prose.\r\n\r\nSigned-off-by: Thomas Fossati <thomas.fossati@arm.com>",
